com.k2.Expressions.evaluators

Class GenericEvaluator<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.k2.Expressions.evaluators.SimpleParameterEvaluator
      • com.k2.Expressions.evaluators.GenericEvaluator<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the value source from which this evaluator will daw the values for getter expressions.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Evaluator, GetterEvaluator<E>, ParameterEvaluator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObjectOrParameterEvaluator, ParamterOrObjectEvaluator

    public class GenericEvaluator<E>
extends SimpleParameterEvaluator
implements Evaluator, ParameterEvaluator, GetterEvaluator<E>
    The generic evaluator provides an implementation of the GetterEvaluator interface. It extends the SimpleParameterEvaluator and as such can provide values for parameter expressions and getter expressions.
    Author:
    simon
